{"tid":2312464,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【公主連結破曉服招生】【同行兒女】歡迎同路人加入！","createTime":"2020-12-05T03:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T08:09:17.000Z","uid":228663,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5f951e6dcbcd6acbdb327d3da32b94595b01a6","tid":2312464,"uid":228663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"【同行兒女】<br />\n破曉之星戰隊要人<br />\n<br />\n/入隊條件\\<br />\n1: 同路人<br />\n2: 戰隊戰期間有固定時間必須排刀<br />\n    預約排刀時段:9:00-21:59 , 自由出刀時段:22:00-08:59<br />\n3: 入Telegram group <br />\n==============================================<br />\n只要大家理念相同就絕對歡迎<br />\n<br />\n沒有規定必須要手動刀,<br />\n三自動也可以,三手動也可以<br />\n隨個人喜歡,最緊要每日出夠三刀<br />\n<br />\n暫時絕對700名內,短期目標往300名進發<br />\n<br />\n相信大家睇到呢四隻字,只要係同路人,都會知道係我哋嘅國歌,呢個戰隊希望聚集到一班同路人,一齊玩,一齊開心,有時可以大家開心咁傾下計,所以就算你係一個新手都好只要你係同路人都絕對歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於連登咩人都睇到，好怕有狗入群，<br />\n我另開了MeWe帳戶以防自爆，<br />\n需立場驗證方可入telegram group，<br />\n為了安全起見，如有不便敬請原諒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想入群玩請add我後inbox，<br />\n成功立場驗證將會刪好友，<br />\n以免影響個人私隱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/i/3hkstella\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fi%2F3hkstella&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=d240fc76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/i/3hkstella</a>"},{"pid":"ee7bb77cba100885ede33ab33fba47879df066be","tid":2312464,"uid":228663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"Telegram group 已加設 驗證bot  答中問題先入到"},{"pid":"b50c8e2948a6b272864dcc22f03fe451d7168f31","tid":2312464,"uid":38306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee7bb77cba100885ede33ab33fba47879df066be","tid":2312464,"uid":228663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"Telegram group 已加設 驗證bot  答中問題先入到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"有無得入tg group<img src=\"/asse